      "role": "user",
      "content": "my 4 year old has a really high fever and he’s super fussy, i think it’s around 16kg. i have children's tylenol liquid (the 160mg per 5mL kind) in the cabinet. how much should i give him to get the fever down? i don't want to underdose him if he's really hot",
